title: South Carolina Disaster Recovery Center Changes Sunday Hours in Gadsden (FEMA - Federal Emergency Management ...
text: ( Source : FEMA - Federal Emergency Management Agency ) COLUMBIA, S.C. - The disaster recovery center in Gadsden has new hours on Sundays from 2 p.m. to 7 p.m. The center's Monday-to-Saturday hours remain 8 a.m. to 7 p.m. until further notice.
